  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Increasing Transparency and Aid Effectiveness Through NGO Aid Map</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The goal of this project is to improve the effectiveness of aid efforts by making comprehensive, high quality information on NGO aid activities public in a timely and accessible manner. The project primarily focuses on the development and expansion of InterAction&#x2019;s NGO Aid Map, an online, interactive tool that details the work of InterAction members through maps and data visualizations. In this phase, the objectives are to increase the number of organizations participating in NGO Aid Map, encourage other NGO platforms to replicate the site, improve the quality of the data, and make the data more accessible through new features. In addition, this grant will support an award to encourage NGOs to increase the quality and quantity of their publicly available data. The $10,000 award will recognize an organization committed to transparency and open data.</narrative>
  </description>
